lead_paragraph: To get a sense of how much the landscape in golf is changing, consider the PGA Tour schedule next year. The Asia swing in October will have as many tournaments as the Florida swing in March.

headline.print_headline: Golf's Landscape Has New Look as PGA Tour Heads to Asia
